headline: Google’s Latest AI Push Hits Travel Stocks. Why They Can Rebound.
summary: Shares of Booking and Expedia were both down by percentages in the mid-single digits on Monday afternoon.

headline: Expedia And Booking Stocks Slide As Google Expand AI Travel Planning Tools
summary: Google will soon bring hotel, flight and other type of reservations bookings into its AI-powered search offering.  The news sent shares of Expedia Group and Booking Holdings falling Monday.  The online search giant said in a blog post Monday that its AI Mode tab has new features to help build custom travel plans.
